  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/01d557ad3e7f2a8cfa7b80c44c74454c.avif?t=1751827158\" width=616 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/49ef73014a63a4e51f5b18dc0f2d0247.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/49ef73014a63a4e51f5b18dc0f2d0247.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/49ef73014a63a4e51f5b18dc0f2d0247.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find core of the same type that are close to each other and blast them.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn more points by blasting cores fast.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Blast Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast the cores however you want.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Click<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/2832be3f13f1880b3dc07ea7dc8d38c5.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=200 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/2832be3f13f1880b3dc07ea7dc8d38c5.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/2832be3f13f1880b3dc07ea7dc8d38c5.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Draw<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/4ea2b6d1b7c31887a6b5fc3bdbcd9e78.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=200 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/4ea2b6d1b7c31887a6b5fc3bdbcd9e78.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/4ea2b6d1b7c31887a6b5fc3bdbcd9e78.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Switch<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/6417b2809d15703e99a730447108f13a.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=200 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/6417b2809d15703e99a730447108f13a.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/6417b2809d15703e99a730447108f13a.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>500 Stages and 20+ Mechanics</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Complete 500 stages by completing various objectives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Take advantage of special impacts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With free mode, you can do it without moves or time limits. But you only earn 1 emblem.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Duel</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blast the cores to damage and defeat your opponent.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Improve your mastery by defeating opponents.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=618 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8 Different Challenge</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points against the move limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points against the time limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Proceed to the next level by reaching the goal score.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In closed core spawn, break as many cores as you can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points by distinguishing colorless cores from their symbols.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points by distinguishing randomly colored cores from their symbols.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points by breaking targeted cores.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Earn points by breaking the resulting explosives.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take your place on the leaderboard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Free Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keep blasting cores as many times as you want without any limitations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Start free mode with the settings you want.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.poster.avif?t=1751827158\" width=618 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.webm?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/8f6a56addfc62ff08c0e0d651ffb4129.mp4?t=1751827158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Boost Impacts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can't pass a stage?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use boost impacts.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mixer :</strong> Mixes all the cores.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Breaker :</strong> Affects object in the selected cell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Horizontal Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row as the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Vertical Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same column as the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Bomb :</strong> Affects objects within 1 unit of the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dedector :</strong> Affects cores that are the same as the selected core type.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Double Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row and column as the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Large Laser :</strong> Affects objects in the same row and column within 1 unit of the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Large Bomb :</strong> Affects objects within 4 unit of the selected core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dedector-Laser :</strong> Converts cores that match the selected core type to lasers and detonates lasers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Dedector-Bomb :</strong> Converts cores that match the selected core type to bombs and detonates bombs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Cleaner :</strong> Affects objects in all cells.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To use boost impacts :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/7064397e45c4c88792fe3414f9f8e554.avif?t=1751827158\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can purchase boost impacts from the boost shop.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/d8b4163c361309edcbe9927d1893a2b7.avif?t=1751827158\" width=616 height=282 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can gain boost impacts by opening various chests.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start blasting the cores.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721550/extras/7694aad518c9e8c17b3a4065a8135d87.webp?t=1751827158\" width=616 height=58 /></span></p>",
